[b][size=140]Tables[/size][/b]

BBCode doesn’t render tables, nor allows it raw HTML tags. The only solution for rendering thus is rendering them as ASCII tables, but it gets the job done.

[code]+-----------+------------------+-----------+
| Heading 1 |    Heading 2     | Heading 3 |
+-----------+------------------+-----------+
| left      |     centered     |     right |
| groovy    |   this is text   |   radical |
| Unicod€   | Slagsmålsklubben |    Piñata |
+-----------+------------------+-----------+[/code]
within [u][code][/u] tags.

